research/history/logs/agent_round_0093.stdout.log:4220:research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0158.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"该 family 的最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可离线导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终重构仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r157 已在当前低 EF 主线下再次给出 adam 的爆炸性负信号，因此 optimizer 分支可视为已被明确关闭。按推荐顺序，下一步应转向 loss/preprocess 轴；本轮只回答一个问题：在保持 family、EF、K、主优化器和 LR 不变的前提下，完全去掉 auxiliary K loss（AUXK_ALPHA=0.0）是否能减少对主重构目标的干扰，带来更好的曲线形状或至少确认该辅助项在当前可部署 regime 下已无必要。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 在不恶化吞吐与总时长的前提下改善曲线或终点，则下一轮做一次同配方 clean repeat 确认。","若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 与基线几乎等价，则记录 auxiliary loss 在该 regime 下非关键，随后再考虑更贴近系统成本的 K 轴。","若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 明显退化，则恢复默认辅助项并结束 loss 轴试探。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 下 selection_cost 仍在预算内；本轮不改 EF、K、TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或其他成本轴，只隔离 auxiliary loss 效应。","r157 在当前主线 regime 下再次复现了 adam 的强负信号，optimizer 分支应正式关闭。","评估本轮必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，区分是否存在由训练更长或吞吐异常造成的假信号。"],"primary_variable":"auxk_alpha","self_review":"这轮严格只改一个主变量 AUXK_ALPHA，family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部固定，符合单变量原则。当前策略顺序在 optimizer 之后本就应转向 loss/preprocess，而 r157 已把 optimizer 问题回答得足够清楚；因此继续停留在 optimizer 分支价值很低，不如用最小改动检查辅助损失在当前低成本主线中的必要性。","summary":"继续围绕主线 family 推进，不开新 family；在 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3 固定的前提下，仅将 AUXK_ALPHA 设为 0.0，判断去掉 auxiliary K loss 是否能改善当前可部署 regime 的训练曲线或确认其已无必要。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0093.stdout.log:4294:research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0157.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u8be5 family \u7684\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\u3002\u5176\u4e2d U(Vx) \u53ef\u79bb\u7ebf\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{c_m} \u4e3a\u9759\u6001 soft-codebook \u5e93\uff0c{b_i} \u4e3a\u9759\u6001 residual \u5b57\u5178\u5e93\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u4ecd\u662f\u591a\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b\u7684 encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 1.25x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002r153-r155 \u5df2\u5148\u540e\u8865\u9f50 clean baseline \u5e76\u628a signum \u7684 LR \u66f2\u7ebf\u770b\u6e05\uff0c3.3e-3 \u867d\u6709\u5c0f\u5e45\u7a33\u5b9a\u6536\u76ca\uff0c\u4f46\u5f53\u524d\u7b56\u7565\u987a\u5e8f\u8981\u6c42\u5728 LR \u4e4b\u540e\u5148\u56de\u7b54 optimizer \u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u4e14 r156 \u7684 K \u8f74\u5c1d\u8bd5\u5df2\u88ab policy \u62e6\u622a\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf OPTIMIZER\uff1a\u4fdd\u6301 family\u3001EF\u3001K\u3001LR \u4e0e\u5bfc\u51fa\u5f62\u5f0f\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u4ec5\u5c06\u4f18\u5316\u5668\u4ece signum \u5207\u5230 adam\uff0c\u56de\u7b54\u552f\u4e00\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u540c\u6837\u7684\u53ef\u90e8\u7f72\u4f4e\u6210\u672c regime \u4e0b\uff0coptimizer \u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u4ecd\u6709\u503c\u5f97\u4fdd\u7559\u7684\u66f2\u7ebf\u5f62\u72b6\u6216\u7ec8\u70b9\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u5e94\u88ab\u518d\u6b21\u660e\u786e\u5173\u95ed\u3002",
